        84.51° Taps DataRobot for a More Personalized Experience for Kroger Shoppers

        84.51° is a retail data science, insights and media company. They help the Kroger company, consumer packaged goods companies, agencies, publishers and affiliated partners create more personalized and valuable experiences for shoppers across the path to purchase.
        Powered by cutting edge science, they leverage 1st-party retail data from over 62 million U.S. households to fuel a more customer-centric journey utilizing 84.51° Insights, 84.51° Loyalty Marketing, and our retail media advertising solution, Kroger Precision Marketing.

        See the Story
